%    instruction \enquote{\cs{foo}|\{bar\}|} never executes.
%    On the contrary, it executes if both packages are loaded,
%    in whatever order.
%    Of course, \pkg{pkg1} must document the hook named
%    |pkg1/on/foo:1| if it is public.
%
